entries.title_d: Destroy the captured Engineer transport in the Dantooine system. The location of another transport has been found. Destroy this transport as well.
entries.title: Dantooine System: Destroy the Captured Engineer Transport. Part II
entries.split_quest_alert: The Inquisition officer requests that we capture the last transport and bring it back so he can question the Bothan spies.
entries.quest_target_d: Destroy the second captured Engineer transport in the Dantooine system to avoid allowing it to fall into enemy hands.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dantooine system and intercept the captured Engineer transport.
entries.quest_escort_d: All the Bothan pilots that are with the transport must also be destroyed.
entries.failed_escape: We lost the transport. Now there is nothing to stop them from delivering it to the Rebellion. Report your failure to your superior officer immediately.
entries.destroy_escort: Some of the transport's escort still remain. Send a message and destroy them as well.
entries.assassinate_success: Excellent. We are now only missing one transport.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Sending the location to your navigation computer. Be alert, they are aware of your presence.
entries.arrival_phase_1: Getting a lock on the second transport. Once you have the location destroy it and all that fly with it.
